# Multi-Feature AI Implementation Plan (Groq-Exclusive)

This plan details the implementation strategy and model selection for the 12 selected AI features for Smart Avenue, using **exclusively** top-tier open-source models available on **Groq**.

## Model Selection (Groq Only)

We will leverage Groq's high-speed inference for all features, prioritizing reasoning and creative performance using leading open-source LLMs.

| Feature | Primary Groq Model | Alternative/Fallback | Purpose |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| 1. Smart Snap & Shop | **Llama 3.2 90B Vision** | Llama 3.2 11B Vision | Image understanding and product identifying. |
| 2. AI Personal Stylist | **DeepSeek-R1 Distill Llama 70B** | Llama 3.3 70B | Logical matching and complex fashion reasoning. |
| 3. Gift Concierge | **DeepSeek-R1 Distill Qwen 32B** | Llama 3.3 70B | Thinking through personalized gift logic. |
| 4. Voice Shopping | **Whisper-large-v3-turbo** | Whisper-large-v3 | Near-instant speech-to-text. |
| 5. Smart Deal Explainer | **Llama 3.1 8B** | Gemma 2 9B | Fast reasoning for sales triggers. |
| 7. AI Sentiment Summarizer| **Llama 3.3 70B** | Mixtral 8x7B | Processing large context reviews. |
| 8. Vibe Check | **Llama 3.3 70B** | DeepSeek-R1 Distill Llama 70B | Abstract semantic mood mapping. |
| 9. Local Language Assistant| **Llama 3.3 70B** | Llama 3.1 8B | Superior multilingual chat performance. |
| 10. Restock Tracker | **Llama 3.1 8B** | Llama 3.2 1B | Lightweight alert generation. |
| 12. Compare & Contrast | **DeepSeek-R1 Distill Llama 70B** | Llama 3.3 70B | Nuanced difference detection. |
| 16. Out of Stock Predictor | **Llama 3.1 8B** | Gemma 2 9B | Rapid notification logic. |
| 20. Social Proof Gen | **Llama 3.1 8B** | Llama 3.2 3B | Creative snippet generation. |


