## Feature Placement & UI/UX Integration

Each feature will be integrated into specific areas of the app to maximize visibility and utility.

### Phase 1: Core Conversion Boosters
| Feature | UI Location | Trigger/Interaction |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Social Proof Gen** | Homepage & Product Pages | "Trending now" badges and "Purchased recently" labels. |
| **Smart Deal Explainer**| Product Detail Page | A "Smart Insight" box directly below the discount price. |
| **Sentiment Summarizer**| Reviews Section | An "AI Review Summary" tab appearing above the list of reviews. |

### Phase 2: Personalized Guidance
| Feature | UI Location | Trigger/Interaction |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **AI Personal Stylist** | "Stylist" Navigation Tab | A dedicated full-page experience for outfit matching. |
| **Gift Concierge** | "Gift Finder" Page | An interactive multi-step questionnaire to find the perfect gift. |
| **Compare & Contrast** | Product Detail / Comparison Dialog | A "Compare with similar" button that opens an AI analysis side-by-side. |

### Phase 3: Interactive Search
| Feature | UI Location | Trigger/Interaction |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Smart Snap & Shop** | Main Search Bar | A "Camera" icon that opens the camera/upload UI. |
| **Voice Shopping** | Main Search Bar | A "Microphone" icon for hands-free searching. |
| **Local Language Asst.** | Global Chat Widget | Language selector in the chat settings or via auto-detect. |
| **Vibe Check** | Homepage Banners | "Shop the Mood" sliders (e.g., Casual, Party, Professional). |

### Phase 4: Proactive Notifications
| Feature | UI Location | Trigger/Interaction |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Restock Tracker** | Product Page / Notifications | "Notify Me" button on OOS items; WhatsApp/Push notification. |
| **OOS Predictor** | Product Page | "Buy soon! Likely to sell out by [Date]" banner on low-stock items. |

